snippet.title: SMALL DOGS bring the BIGGEST LAUGHS - Super FUNNY DOG videos
snippet.description:
I swear this is the hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Small dogs are so super funny, they just never fail to make us laugh! Really great and hilarious pets! Look how all these small dogs fail, make funny sounds, play, sleep,... So super funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
